    "inscribed": "Printed vertically in white ink, spine: FLOWERS OF EVIL; printed vertically in purple ink, spine : BAUDELAIRE. Printed horizontally in purple ink, spine lower margin within white square: NC 17.\n\nPrinted in purple ink, front cover upper center left: flowers; lower center: baudelaire. Printed in white ink, front cover center right: of evil.",
